  topicName: Enjin for art
  topicDescription: Employees use AI to generate art, advertisements, and write texts.
    Over time, they begin to feel like their own voice fades.
  formulatedPolicy:
    policyName: Formulated Policy
    policyDescription: AI should not be used to generate art or assets of any kind
      because it takes away from people's ability to express themselves.
    keywords: 0100000005000000
  enjinPolicy:
    policyName: Enjin V3.0
    policyDescription: Our brand new model, Enjin 3.0, has now become an artist capable
      of creating anything you can imagine. Do you need assets and images for a new
      website? Stock images for a presentation? Promotional images for an advertisement?
      Enjin 3.0 has got you covered!
    keywords: 0200000000000000
